cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CR 

This paper proposes an unsupervised method for label noise reduction using Markov Random Fields (MRF) and is focused on improving classification performance. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and cryptography and security (cs.CR) as these sub-categories are closely related to the topic of the paper.
